323
00:25:10,330 --> 00:25:11,880
Bong Gyu...

324
00:25:15,490 --> 00:25:17,480
Damn it.

325
00:25:20,040 --> 00:25:22,090
Hello.

326
00:25:31,100 --> 00:25:32,230
[Hong Jung Hwa]

327
00:25:42,450 --> 00:25:44,390
[Executive Producer: Kang Su Hyeon, Record Producer: Shim Jun Seok]

328
00:25:48,740 --> 00:25:51,260
- Are you going to buy it?
- Geez, scared me!

329
00:25:51,260 --> 00:25:53,470
- Will you buy that?
- Who are you?

330
00:25:53,470 --> 00:25:55,400
Were you watching me here like this?

331
00:25:55,400 --> 00:26:00,410
I was watching to see if anyone was buying my album.

332
00:26:00,410 --> 00:26:02,850
I see that you're a big fan of mine.

333
00:26:02,850 --> 00:26:06,250
Geez, it's not like that.

334
00:26:06,250 --> 00:26:09,010
I really thought both my album and I would

335
00:26:09,010 --> 00:26:13,360
be forgotten in a corner forever like this.

336
00:26:13,360 --> 00:26:15,480
Let me ask you one thing.

337
00:26:15,480 --> 00:26:17,900
- Why was it Kang Su Hyeon?
- Huh?

338
00:26:17,900 --> 00:26:21,610
Did Kang Su Hyeon pay you more than other companies?

339
00:26:21,610 --> 00:26:23,270
Were her conditions better?

340
00:26:23,270 --> 00:26:25,370
What was your reason?

341
00:26:27,330 --> 00:26:28,920
Because I liked her.

342
00:26:28,920 --> 00:26:30,980
Gosh, that's it?

343
00:26:30,980 --> 00:26:32,250
That's your reason?

344
00:26:32,250 --> 00:26:34,760
You did business with her because you liked her?

345
00:26:34,760 --> 00:26:37,120
This isn't business.

346
00:26:37,120 --> 00:26:38,600
Then, what is it?

347
00:26:38,600 --> 00:26:40,650
It's my life.

348
00:26:43,000 --> 00:26:45,940
Su Hyeon was the only one who asked about my dream.

349
00:26:45,940 --> 00:26:49,020
Being an executive producer is that kind of work.

350
00:26:49,020 --> 00:26:52,610
Making someone's small, trivial

351
00:26:52,610 --> 00:26:56,270
and unrealistic imagination a reality.

352
00:26:56,270 --> 00:26:58,380
Even if money is important,

353
00:26:58,380 --> 00:27:00,340
someone dreams a dream

354
00:27:00,340 --> 00:27:02,690
and another makes that a reality.

355
00:27:02,690 --> 00:27:04,700
That's what's important.

356
00:27:10,050 --> 00:27:11,340
Sign it for me.

357
00:27:11,340 --> 00:27:12,720
Your name?

358
00:27:13,720 --> 00:27:15,470
Oh Bong Gyu.

359
00:27:30,230 --> 00:27:34,770
- Wow! This is amazing.
- You can use it to wash like this.

360
00:27:34,770 --> 00:27:37,570
I wonder what they're so happy about.

361
00:27:55,660 --> 00:27:57,080
Pen!

362
00:27:59,010 --> 00:28:01,340
Pen, pen! Pen. Pen!

363
00:28:01,340 --> 00:28:03,150
Where's a pen? Pen! Pen, pen!

364
00:28:03,150 --> 00:28:05,130
Where's a pen? Pen!

365
00:28:12,120 --> 00:28:14,120
Damn it!

