377
00:29:24,200 --> 00:29:26,040
Never mind, Unni.

378
00:29:26,040 --> 00:29:27,900
I'll hang up.

379
00:29:53,710 --> 00:29:55,220
What is it?

380
00:29:55,960 --> 00:29:57,580
Oh, dinner?

