00:33:00,530 --> 00:33:04,320
♫ <i>Smile again</i> ♫

412
00:33:04,320 --> 00:33:07,860
♫ <i>Just like right now</i> ♫

413
00:33:27,540 --> 00:33:29,410
You're late.

414
00:33:31,300 --> 00:33:35,600
I definitely told you that I'll sell him to whoever comes first.

415
00:33:42,600 --> 00:33:46,010
When you receive the contract from TA, deposit the money right away.

416
00:33:48,220 --> 00:33:49,620
What?

417
00:34:12,020 --> 00:34:13,880
Jang Hyeon Cheol.

418
00:34:13,880 --> 00:34:18,160
The Board of Directors unanimously voted to dismiss you as the CEO as of today.

419
00:34:19,910 --> 00:34:21,700
You know the reason and procedure for dismissal,

420
00:34:21,700 --> 00:34:24,300
since you saw it happen during Kang Su Hyeon's dismissal, right?

421
00:34:30,320 --> 00:34:33,000
Will you be able to fire me?

422
00:34:33,000 --> 00:34:37,970
The amount of poison I released into this company isn't small.

423
00:34:37,970 --> 00:34:41,710
I am cutting you out before that poison spreads further

424
00:34:41,710 --> 00:34:43,860
and makes the company useless.

425
00:34:44,860 --> 00:34:49,390
CEO Kim, do you want to ruin your son's life like this?

426
00:34:54,220 --> 00:34:55,520
Your druggie son.

427
00:34:55,520 --> 00:34:58,670
Do you want him to live as an ex-con at such a young age?

428
00:34:58,670 --> 00:35:00,440
You should protect your son!

429
00:35:00,440 --> 00:35:05,370
That's right. I should protect my own son.

430
00:35:11,840 --> 00:35:13,290
<i>This is the Narcotics Unit of Gangnam Police Station.</i>

431
00:35:13,290 --> 00:35:16,950
I am CEO Kim Dong Jun of Pandora Entertainment.

432
00:35:16,950 --> 00:35:19,580
I want to report a drug offender.

433
00:35:19,580 --> 00:35:20,940
<i>Pardon?</i>

434
00:35:23,220 --> 00:35:25,330
<i>Okay, please tell me.</i>

435
00:35:25,330 --> 00:35:29,790
Kim Jin Hyeon.

436
00:35:30,790 --> 00:35:32,940
It's my son.

437
00:35:40,630 --> 00:35:46,000
This is how I protect my son.

438
00:35:46,000 --> 00:35:51,260
Hyeon Cheol, don't become more miserable.

439
00:35:51,260 --> 00:35:54,290
The more misery you cause others,

440
00:35:54,290 --> 00:35:58,750
the more miserable your life becomes.

441
00:36:01,880 --> 00:36:04,190
Tell Kang Su Hyeon

442
00:36:05,480 --> 00:36:10,280
that I'll show her what true misery is like.

443
00:36:18,330 --> 00:36:20,250
Thanks.

444
00:36:20,250 --> 00:36:22,520
I didn't do it for your benefit.

445
00:36:22,520 --> 00:36:27,100
I felt like it would also hurt me if I let that crazy bastard be.

446
00:36:32,770 --> 00:36:34,370
I'll be going.

447
00:36:54,100 --> 00:36:57,940
Now, your contract with TA has been taken care of.

448
00:36:57,940 --> 00:36:59,540
Really?

449
00:37:00,440 --> 00:37:02,370
CEO Kang sacrificed a lot.

450
00:37:02,370 --> 00:37:05,690
She sold the factory and...

451
00:37:08,750 --> 00:37:10,610
Call her yourself.

452
00:37:32,050 --> 00:37:33,900
<i>Thank you.</i>

453
00:38:04,640 --> 00:38:06,320
What is it?

454
00:38:07,400 --> 00:38:09,410
I'll pay you back.

455
00:38:09,410 --> 00:38:11,730
I'm the one who borrowed this money.

456
00:38:11,730 --> 00:38:14,210
Don't contact Su Hyeon.

457
00:38:15,920 --> 00:38:21,460
Is it that difficult for you guys to bow your head once to your parent?

458
00:38:21,460 --> 00:38:24,330
Have you ever considered her as your daughter?

459
00:38:26,590 --> 00:38:31,000
You two do not have a normal parent-child relationship.

460
00:38:32,080 --> 00:38:33,980
Why were you...

461
00:38:35,000 --> 00:38:37,460
Why were you so mean to her?

462
00:38:37,460 --> 00:38:42,300
Do you know how much she suffered, unable to tell anyone,

463
00:38:42,300 --> 00:38:46,120
living with a crushed heart like that?

464
00:38:52,890 --> 00:38:55,260
Still, I am her father.

465
00:38:56,260 --> 00:39:01,030
She should apologize to her father first.

466
00:39:05,390 --> 00:39:07,260
With this money,

467
00:39:08,690 --> 00:39:11,680
I will save a kid who's like a son to us.

468
00:39:13,020 --> 00:39:14,830
Thank you.

469
00:39:16,410 --> 00:39:17,970
I will...

470
00:39:19,050 --> 00:39:21,240
pay back the money

471
00:39:22,510 --> 00:39:24,420
by the deadline.

472
00:39:49,440 --> 00:39:51,550
You know Producer Park Ji Cheol, who was investigated for

473
00:39:51,550 --> 00:39:53,530
manipulating an audition program, right?

474
00:39:53,530 --> 00:39:57,200
He passed out from drug withdrawal symptoms, and he confessed.

475
00:40:00,080 --> 00:40:01,580
What did he confess?

476
00:40:01,580 --> 00:40:06,310
That he took drugs at Muse, the nightclub you run.

477
00:40:08,210 --> 00:40:11,990
<i>Yes. Muse.</i>

478
00:40:11,990 --> 00:40:16,140
<i>There, I can get drugs,</i>

479
00:40:16,140 --> 00:40:19,940
<i>and I am provided a space to do it.</i>

480
00:40:20,880 --> 00:40:22,750
You believe the words of a druggie?

481
00:40:22,750 --> 00:40:25,210
Investigating solely on what they tell you is problematic.

482
00:40:25,210 --> 00:40:26,840
I don't believe everything they say. I do check.

483
00:40:26,840 --> 00:40:28,200
I do check for myself.

484
00:40:28,200 --> 00:40:31,370
Is it true that drugs are dealt with or taken at Muse?

485
00:40:31,370 --> 00:40:33,470
It's false.

486
00:40:33,470 --> 00:40:35,220
Then, how about this one?

487
00:40:36,000 --> 00:40:38,260
<i>After taking drugs at Muse,</i>

488
00:40:38,260 --> 00:40:41,060
<i>we all went to Sheon Hotel.</i>

489
00:40:41,060 --> 00:40:46,020
<i>In one car, there were about five of us.</i>

490
00:40:46,020 --> 00:40:51,640
<i>And another car had someone who looked like a high schooler</i>

491
00:40:51,640 --> 00:40:56,390
<i>with a handsome face driving it.</i>

492
00:40:57,970 --> 00:41:00,180
This is all nonsense.

493
00:41:00,180 --> 00:41:03,690
Words of a druggie cant be evidence. Why are you doing this?

494
00:41:03,690 --> 00:41:05,810
Then, let's check.

495
00:41:05,810 --> 00:41:09,190
Nightclub Muse is undergoing search and seizure right now.

496
00:41:18,990 --> 00:41:20,810
Who are you guys?

497
00:41:20,810 --> 00:41:22,430
We are the police.

