00:43:07,730 --> 00:43:09,100
Yeah.

513
00:43:16,410 --> 00:43:18,220
Okay, you can return.

514
00:43:22,080 --> 00:43:25,180
Jang Hyeon Cheol, you will be summoned again soon.

515
00:43:25,180 --> 00:43:27,580
Don't go anywhere far.

